PURPOSE AND SCOPE:

This software framework is intended solely for repairing and adapting drivers 
to work with the subject's operating system (not Windows/Microsoft). The 
framework provides tools for driver analysis and reimplementation to enable 
hardware compatibility with non-Windows operating systems.

